<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 03:14:58 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>东京世锦赛男子和女子 100 米决赛定于第二天举行</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/athletics/mens-womens-100m-finals-scheduled-day-two-tokyo-world-championships-2024-08-01/</link><description>世界田径理事会（WAC）周三表示，男子和女子 100 米决赛将于明年在东京举行的世界田径锦标赛第二天举行。</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 02:41:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/athletics/mens-womens-100m-finals-scheduled-day-two-tokyo-world-championships-2024-08-01/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲股市延续全球涨势，日经指数因日元飙升而表现异常</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-08-01/</link><description>亚洲股市周四上涨，跟随 Meta 和 Nvidia 帮助下的全球科技股大幅复苏，而美国即将放松政策的前景提振了全球债券和大宗商品。</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 02:06:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-08-01/</guid></item><item><title>财新PMI显示，中国工厂活动九个月来首次收缩</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-factory-activity-contracts-first-time-9-months-caixin-pmi-shows-2024-08-01/</link><description>周四的一项私营部门调查显示，由于新订单下降，中国 7 月份制造业活动出现九个月来首次萎缩，这对该国 2024 年下半年的增长势头不利。</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 01:52:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-factory-activity-contracts-first-time-9-months-caixin-pmi-shows-2024-08-01/</guid></item><item><title>加拿大军舰穿越台湾海峡，激怒中国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/canadian-warship-passes-through-taiwan-strait-drawing-chinas-ire-2024-08-01/</link><description>一艘加拿大军舰通过台湾海峡，渥太华称这是对开放的印太地区的承诺，此举遭到中国指责，称 7 月 31 日的海军演习破坏了和平。</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 01:29:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/canadian-warship-passes-through-taiwan-strait-drawing-chinas-ire-2024-08-01/</guid></item><item><title>中国外交部称中印将加快边界谈判</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-india-speed-up-border-talks-says-chinese-foreign-ministry-2024-08-01/</link><description>中国外交部周四在一份声明中表示，中印将加快围绕有争议边界的谈判，继续维护该地区的和平与安宁。</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 00:07:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-india-speed-up-border-talks-says-chinese-foreign-ministry-2024-08-01/</guid></item><item><title>乌克兰泽连斯基希望中国对俄罗斯施加更大压力</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/zelenskiy-says-ukraine-does-not-want-china-mediator-2024-07-31/</link><description>乌克兰总统泽连斯基周三表示，基辅不希望中国在与俄罗斯长达29个月的冲突中充当调解人，但希望北京向莫斯科施加更大压力，以结束战争。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 22:17:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/zelenskiy-says-ukraine-does-not-want-china-mediator-2024-07-31/</guid></item><item><title>早间出价：非凡的反弹席卷了所有市场</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-07-31/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 21:47:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-07-31/</guid></item><item><title>游泳——中国选手潘金莲打破自己保持的1亿米自由泳金牌世界纪录</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/swimming-chinas-pan-obliterates-100m-freestyle-world-record-gold-2024-07-31/</link><description>周三，中国选手潘占乐在巴黎奥运会上打破了自己保持的100米自由泳世界纪录，在该项目中夺得了令人震惊的金牌，并击败了众多冠军对手。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 20:53:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/swimming-chinas-pan-obliterates-100m-freestyle-world-record-gold-2024-07-31/</guid></item><item><title>美国立法者寻求阻止中国企业获得太阳能制造补贴</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/us-lawmakers-seek-block-chinese-firms-solar-manufacturing-subsidy-2024-07-31/</link><description>美国两党议员小组周三提出了一项法案，禁止中国太阳能电池板制造商为其美国工厂申请补贴。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 19:52:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/us-lawmakers-seek-block-chinese-firms-solar-manufacturing-subsidy-2024-07-31/</guid></item><item><title>中国反兴奋剂机构指责《纽约时报》蓄意破坏报道</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/china-anti-doping-agency-accuses-new-york-times-sabotage-over-latest-report-2024-07-31/</link><description>中国反兴奋剂机构（CHINADA）指责《纽约时报》将兴奋剂问题政治化，并表示该刊物试图“影响巴黎奥运会上中国运动员的心理”。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 19:37:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/china-anti-doping-agency-accuses-new-york-times-sabotage-over-latest-report-2024-07-31/</guid></item><item><title>彭博新闻称，美国考虑对中国获取人工智能存储芯片实施新限制</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/us-mulls-new-curbs-chinas-access-ai-memory-chips-bloomberg-news-says-2024-07-31/</link><description>据彭博社周三报道，美国正在考虑单方面限制中国获取人工智能存储芯片，例如美光科技和 SK 海力士制造的芯片以及能够制造此类半导体的设备，最快将于下个月进行。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 18:13:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/us-mulls-new-curbs-chinas-access-ai-memory-chips-bloomberg-news-says-2024-07-31/</guid></item><item><title>国防部长称加拿大军舰通过台湾海峡</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/canadian-warship-transited-through-taiwan-strait-defense-minister-says-2024-07-31/</link><description>加拿大国防部长表示，一艘加拿大军舰最近通过台湾海峡，重申了加拿大对“自由、开放和包容”的印太地区的承诺。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 16:06:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/canadian-warship-transited-through-taiwan-strait-defense-minister-says-2024-07-31/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾与美国海军在南海举行联合演习</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/philippines-us-navy-hold-joint-exercise-south-china-sea-2024-07-31/</link><description>菲律宾武装部队表示，菲律宾和美国海军周三在南海举行了联合海上演习。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 12:49:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/philippines-us-navy-hold-joint-exercise-south-china-sea-2024-07-31/</guid></item><item><title>BMX-阿根廷和中国队在自由泳比赛中夺得金牌，热门球队惨遭淘汰</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/cycling/bmx-chinas-deng-takes-gold-womens-freestyle-2024-07-31/</link><description>周三，在巴黎炎热的阳光下，首次参加奥运会的阿根廷和中国选手在 BMX 自由式决赛中夺得金牌，一连串戏剧性的撞车事故将卫冕奖牌得主击倒。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 12:14:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/cycling/bmx-chinas-deng-takes-gold-womens-freestyle-2024-07-31/</guid></item><item><title>中国预计未来五年城镇化率接近70%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-expects-urbanisation-rate-near-70-next-five-years-2024-07-31/</link><description>据官方媒体报道，中国国务院周三表示，预计未来五年常住人口城镇化率将提高到接近70%。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 11:48:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-expects-urbanisation-rate-near-70-next-five-years-2024-07-31/</guid></item></channel></rss>